NAME
    Template::Plugin::Text::Widont - A Template Toolkit filter for removing
    typographic widows

SYNOPSIS
        [% USE Text::Widont nbsp => 'html' %]
        [% "If the world didn't suck, we'd all fall off" | widont %]

DESCRIPTION
    "Template::Plugin::Text::Widont" provides a simple Template Toolkit
    filter interface to the Text::Widont module.

    See the NON-BREAKING SPACE TYPES section in Text::Widont's documentation
    for more information about available values for "nbsp".

METHODS
  init
    Overrides the method from Template::Plugin::Filter.

  filter
    Overrides the method from Template::Plugin::Filter.

SEE ALSO
    Template, Template::Plugin::Filter, Text::Widont

DEPENDENCIES
    *   Template::Plugin::Filter

    *   Text::Widont

